<taxonomicName authority="DeLong &amp; Freytag, 1966" authorityName="DeLong &amp; Freytag" authorityYear="1966" box="[388,872,1590,1615]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Acusana" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="536" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hebeta">
<emphasis box="[388,569,1590,1614]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="536">Acusana hebeta</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="DeLong, D. M. &amp; Freytag, P. H." box="[580,872,1590,1615]" pageId="5" pageNumber="536" pagination="42 - 63" refId="ref6076" refString="DeLong, D. M. &amp; Freytag, P. H. (1966) Studies of the Gyponinae: A synopsis of the genus Acusana DeLong. The Ohio Journal of Science, 66 (1), 42 - 63." type="journal article" year="1966">DeLong &amp; Freytag, 1966</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry box="[948,1036,1591,1615]" name="Panama" pageId="5" pageNumber="536">Panamá</collectingCountry>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="DeLong &amp; Freytag, 1966" authorityName="DeLong &amp; Freytag" authorityYear="1966" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Acusana" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="536" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="convesta">
<emphasis box="[1098,1301,1591,1614]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="536">Acusana convesta</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="DeLong, D. M. &amp; Freytag, P. H." pageId="5" pageNumber="536" pagination="42 - 63" refId="ref6076" refString="DeLong, D. M. &amp; Freytag, P. H. (1966) Studies of the Gyponinae: A synopsis of the genus Acusana DeLong. The Ohio Journal of Science, 66 (1), 42 - 63." type="journal article" year="1966">DeLong &amp; Freytag, 1966</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry box="[383,553,1626,1651]" name="Guyana" pageId="5" pageNumber="536">British Guiana</collectingCountry>
. However the new species has the aedeagal shaft, in lateral view, broad and straight in contrast to the curved and thinner aedeagus of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="DeLong &amp; Freytag" authorityYear="1966" box="[779,907,1663,1686]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Acusana" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="536" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="convesta">
<emphasis box="[779,907,1663,1686]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="536">A. convesta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="DeLong &amp; Freytag" authorityYear="1966" box="[959,1063,1662,1686]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Acusana" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="536" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hebeta">
<emphasis box="[959,1063,1662,1686]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="536">A. hebeta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName authority="Domahovski &amp; Cavichioli, 2019" authorityName="Domahovski &amp; Cavichioli" authorityYear="2019" box="[1076,1264,1662,1686]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Acusana" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="536" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dilatata" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[1076,1264,1662,1686]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="536">Acusana dilatata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1270,1358,1662,1687]" pageId="5" pageNumber="536">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1270,1358,1662,1687]" pageId="5" pageNumber="536" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
